  "cloudDescStratus":"Stratus clouds are low-level clouds that often cover a large area of the sky in a uniform layer.",
  "cloudDescStratocumulus":"Stratocumulus clouds are low-level clouds with fist-sized cloud masses loosely distributed in clusters.",
  "cloudDescNimbostratus":"Nimbostratus clouds are thick low-level clouds that cover the sky and usually produce continuous rain.",
  "cloudDescCumulus":"Cumulus clouds are low-level clouds with moderate vertical development and rounded tops.",
  "cloudDescCumulonimbus":"Cumulonimbus clouds have strong vertical development and usually produce thunderstorms.",
